      <title>最新民意调查显示，人们对南非未来的乐观情绪有所上升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/optimism-about-south-africa-s-future-has-climbed-new-poll-shows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项调查显示，受到商业友好型联合政府的组建以及连续六个月无停电的鼓舞，对国家未来持乐观态度的南非人数量增加了一倍。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/optimism-about-south-africa-s-future-has-climbed-new-poll-shows</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 13:52:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国总理敦促日本首相在紧张局势中保持两国关系稳定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/chinese-premier-urges-japan-pm-to-keep-ties-steady-amid-tensions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国国务院总理李强敦促日本首相石破茂在紧张局势中保持双边关系“健康、稳定”，并呼吁两国维护全球供应链和自由贸易的稳定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/chinese-premier-urges-japan-pm-to-keep-ties-steady-amid-tensions</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 13:48:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国将非洲核能胜利寄托于技术，加纳则在权衡选择</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/us-pins-africa-nuclear-win-on-technology-as-ghana-weighs-options</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上个月，美国击败俄罗斯，成功建造了加纳首座小型模块化核反应堆。华盛顿认为，这项交易更看重美国技术，而非廉价融资，但加纳对未来的选择仍持开放态度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/us-pins-africa-nuclear-win-on-technology-as-ghana-weighs-options</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 12:22:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>通往 270 的疯狂之路：哈里斯能从特朗普手中夺回阿拉斯加吗？</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/electoral-college-map-alaska-may-play-a-key-role-in-harris-trump-race</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项民意调查显示，在共和党势力雄厚的阿拉斯加州，哈里斯与特朗普的差距不大，但她与阿拉斯加州最近派往国会山的那位民主党人不同。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/electoral-college-map-alaska-may-play-a-key-role-in-harris-trump-race</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 12:00:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>前中国人民银行官员因受贿被判死缓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/ex-pboc-official-gets-suspended-death-sentence-for-taking-bribes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国一家法院对中国人民银行前副行长因收受贿赂逾 3.86 亿元人民币（5460 万美元）判处死缓。这一备受关注的案件体现了习近平主席整顿金融业的决心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/ex-pboc-official-gets-suspended-death-sentence-for-taking-bribes</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 11:42:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
